RECONSIDERATION DOCKET

93-1273. Lunar v. Cleveland.

Cuyahoga County, No. 61968. Reported at 69 Ohio St.3d 673, 635 N.E.2d 357. This cause came on for further consideration upon appellees’ motion for reconsideration. Upon consideration of appellees’ motion to withdraw its motion for reconsideration,

IT IS ORDERED by the court that the motion to withdraw motion for reconsideration be, and the same is hereby, granted, effective August 25, 1994.
